The paper also discusses the use of stochastic connectivity, which is a technique used in machine learning to improve the performance of deep neural networks, and this falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also uses image datasets for experimentation, which falls under the category of cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the paper discusses the potential applications of StochasticNet in various tasks, which falls under the category of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper also discusses the potential benefits of StochasticNet in terms of operational speed, which falls under the category of cs.SY (Systems and Control).
